description: Candelaria Mining Corp. engages in the exploration of gold deposits in Canada and Mexico. It holds 100% interests is the Caballo Blanco Project consists 14 contiguous mining claims covering an area of approximately 19,650 hectares located in state of Zacatecas, Mexico; and the Pinos project consists of 29 mining concessions covering an area of approximately 3,816 hectares located in state of Veracruz, Mexico. The company was formerly known as Branco Resources Ltd. Candelaria Mining Corp. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
